			<h1 id="point-categories">Point categories</h1>
<ul>
<li>Usability</li>
<li>Performance</li>
<li>Visual</li>
<li>Dynamicism</li>
<li>Developer experience</li>
<li>Debugging</li>
<li>Refactoring</li>
</ul>

			</div>
			
