			<div class="themedArea">
			<h1 id="participant-award-request-and-response">Participant Award - Request and response</h1>
<ul>
<li>No dynamicism</li>
<li>User experience depends on load times</li>
<li>Serving full web page from server</li>
<li>Usually built backend first<ul>
<li>J2EE, Controller &amp; JSP</li>
<li>PHP</li>
<li>Etc.</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>

			</div>
			
			<div class="componentContainer " style="top: 526px; left: 435px; -webkit-transform:   ; -moz-transform:   ; transform:   ; width: 375px; height: 211.83px;">
