			<div class=" slideContainer strut-slide-16" style="width: 1024px; height: 768px;">
			<div class="themedArea">
			<h1 id="build-processes-why-should-we-care-">Build Processes - Why should we care?</h1>
<ul>
<li>Performance<ul>
<li>Minification</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>Security<ul>
<li>Uglification</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>New and Improved JavaScript<ul>
<li>Transpilation</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>Quality<ul>
<li>Linting, Static Analysis, Extendability, Refactorability</li>
</ul>
</li>
